messages.message:
We have room for a few more demos at next week's *Demo Day*! If you're interested please sign up here (https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSclMa3sPe_HBN_Y23FHLl0szuXSPl5rO0fruCsZ4U9rEq147g/viewform).

For those who haven't been to Demo Day before:
_Demo Day is a time twice a month where Product and Engineering can showcase projects and features that they have been working on to the rest of the team._
_You can watch previous demo day recordings here (https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/IB/pages/27394369/IB+Demo+Day)!_ :movie_camera:
